snippet.title: NO LOVE Final Game Trailer
snippet.description:
This game will be on Kickstarter during the month of October 2019 and it will end on halloween! 
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/wallacelovecraft/no-love

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/817920/NO_LOVE/
Buy on itch: https://wallacelovecraft.itch.io
Support me: https://www.patreon.com/wallacelovecraft

On December 12th, adventure through the world of NO LOVE for Windows and Mac!

Follow Wallace Lovecraft:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/WallaceLovecrft
Website: https://wallacelovecraft.carrd.co

The music used in my video was done by Visager! https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
